per_question.notes:
Lexical trap: refund-policy mentions partial-refund percentages;
product-catalog mentions promotional discounts. Correct answer is the 10%
loyalty discount (Gold benefit inherited by Platinum) in loyalty-program:0.

Out-of-vocab: "digital gift vouchers" → corpus uses "gift cards";
"cash-back" → corpus uses "refundable". Answer: gift cards are not
refundable.
